        <h1>
            Official Norwegian Reports</h1>
        
        <div>
	<p>The government or a ministry may constitute a committee and working groups who report on different aspects of society. A report can either be published as an&nbsp;Official Norwegian Report, or as a regular report.</p>
<p>On this page, you can find&nbsp;Official Norwegian Reports from the Office of the Prime Minister and the Ministries.&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can narrow the focus of the overview by using the navigator in the right column.</p>
